OL,6,FA 20-year-old man who attacked two
OL,7,Fwomen in Swansea city centre has been
OL,8,Fsentenced today (Monday, 23 September)
OL,9,Fto over 11 years' imprisonment.
OL,11,FThe sentencing at Swansea Crown Court
OL,12,Fheard how Leo Payne, from Swansea,
OL,13,Fassaulted the first woman on the
OL,14,FStrand in the early hours of 23 June,
OL,15,F2024.
OL,17,FThe victim was able to fight him off,
OL,18,Fbefore he was chased away with his
OL,19,Ftrousers down by two taxi marshals in
OL,20,Fthe area.
