OL,7,FWallich, hitting him multiple times
OL,8,Fwith a wine bottle, with one of the
OL,9,Fblows causing a head injury.
OL,11,FDeputy Chief Crown Prosecutor for CPS
OL,12,FCymru-Wales, Iwan Jenkins, said: "Leo
OL,13,FPayne prowled the city centre carrying
OL,14,Fout a campaign of terrifying sexual
OL,15,Fattacks and violent offences.
