OL,6,F"His repeated offending shows that he
OL,7,Fwas an incredible danger to others,
OL,8,Fand there were no signs of any remorse
OL,9,Ffor his actions.
OL,11,F"I would like to pay tribute to his
OL,12,Fvictims for their bravery in coming
OL,13,Fforward to report Leo Payne's actions.
OL,14,FThey will all be dealing with the
OL,15,Funimaginable traumatic effects of his
OL,16,Fcrimes for a long time, but hopefully
OL,17,Fthis sentencing will offer some
OL,18,Freassurance that he will no longer be
OL,19,Fon the streets."
