OL,6,FLeo Payne was sentenced to 11 years
OL,7,Fand three months' imprisonment which
OL,8,Fwas extended with a four years and
OL,9,Fnine months' license period on 20
OL,10,FSeptember 2024 including a requirement
OL,11,Fto register as a sex offender
OL,12,Findefinitely.
OL,14,FThe 20 year old had pleaded guilty to
OL,15,Ftwo counts of attempted rape, one
OL,16,Fcount of sexual assault by
OL,17,Fpenetration, exposure and unlawful
OL,18,Fwounding.
